---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro'
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro'

const lastUpdated = 'June 26, 2025'
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Policy"
    description="Privacy Policy for Modrex, the free and open-source desktop mod manager."
>
    <Nav />
    <main class="legal-page">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="prose">
                <p class="eyebrow">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

                <p>
                    Modrex is built to respect your privacy. This policy covers both the Modrex
                    desktop app and this website (modrex.net).
                </p>

                <h2>Desktop app</h2>
                <p>
                    Modrex does not collect any data by default. The app includes an optional,
                    opt-in analytics feature:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Opt-in only.</strong> You are asked once on first launch and can change
                        your choice at any time in Settings.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>What is collected if you opt in:</strong> anonymous usage events (features
                        used, mods installed, app version, operating system). A random per-install ID
                        is generated locally — it is never linked to your name, email, or any account.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>What is never collected:</strong> file paths, mod search text, game save
                        data, account credentials, or any personally identifying information.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Processor:</strong> analytics data is sent to Google Analytics 4 via a
                        proxy at modrex.net. See <a
                            href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a
                        >.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>If you opt out (or never opt in), no data leaves your device from the app.</p>

                <h2>Website (modrex.net)</h2>
                <p>
                    This website uses Google Analytics 4 with Consent Mode v2. Analytics are denied
                    by default and only enabled if you accept via the cookie banner. We do not use
                    any other tracking, advertising networks, or third-party data brokers.
                </p>

                <h2>Data sharing</h2>
                <p>
                    We do not sell, rent, or trade any data. We do not share data with third parties
                    except as required by the analytics processor described above or by law.
                </p>

                <h2>Data retention</h2>
                <p>
                    Analytics data is retained for 14 months per Google Analytics' default retention
                    settings. You can request deletion by contacting us.
                </p>

                <h2>Your rights</h2>
                <p>
                    You can opt out of analytics at any time in the app's Settings or by declining
                    the cookie banner on this website. Since we collect no personal data, there is
                    nothing to access, correct, or export beyond what you already control locally.
                </p>

                <h2>Changes</h2>
                <p>
                    We may update this policy at any time. The "Last updated" date above will
                    reflect any changes.
                </p>

                <h2>Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    Questions? Open an issue on <a
                        href="https://github.com/modrexio/modrex/issues"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener">GitHub</a
                    > or join our <a
                        href="https://discord.gg/tenzpx8JRM"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener">Discord</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .legal-page {
        padding: 80px 0 96px;
    }

    .prose {
        max-width: 680px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-tertiary);
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }

    h1 {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: var(--tracking-display);
    }

    h2 {
        margin: 40px 0 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--color-text);
    }

    p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    ul {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        padding-left: 20px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
    }

    li {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    a {
        color: var(--color-accent-bright);
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    strong {
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-weight: 500;
    }
</style>
